1. What this it?                           
ÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍÍ  
This is a tiny tool for make ANSI Art      
for develop batch games, make a gif,       
etc; but convertible into various          
formats like ANSI sequences (.pic),        
Colous.exe Dat File (.pbc), Batch Paint    
V1 & V2 Files (.bat), ANSI/ASCII file      
without format (.rtf), Regular expresions  
file (main format [.mpe]).                 
                                           
Can support all the formats said for       
open and save                              
                                           
This program is built-with Seta-GPU engine 
coloured version                           
